Which of the following are the key benefits of Communities?
A. Enables people to work together more effectively
B. Brings people together to a central place to collaborate on projects or topics
C. Facilitates cross-company collaboration since participants can join without paying for a
subscription
D. All of the above
Answer: B
What is the purpose of a part number for an average fee?
A. To bill customers when their stock price exceeds their market value
B. To bill customers whose inbound email exceeds their SPAM threshold
C. To bill customers when they exceed their purchased authorized user entitlement
D. None of the above
Answer: C

A. To bill for Meetings by the minute
B. To bill for a partial month when an order is provisioned before the end of the first month.
C. To credit for days when nobody logs into SmartCloud for Social Business
D. To adjust pricing according to daily exchange rate fluctuations
